Key Enhancements Added:
üéØ Account-Level Drill-Down:
‚úÖ Dashboard Variables - Filter by Account ID and other dimensions
‚úÖ Account-Specific Metrics - All widgets now support account filtering
‚úÖ Cross-Account Comparison - Side-by-side account analysis

üìä Detailed Breakdowns:
‚úÖ OS-Specific Data - Windows/Linux/MacOS patch compliance
‚úÖ Resource Type Analysis - EBS/RDS/EFS backup protection
‚úÖ Severity Breakdowns - Critical/High/Medium patch exceptions
‚úÖ Top Failures - Most failing instances and failure reasons

üîç Granular Visibility:
‚úÖ Individual Instance Data - Specific failing instances
‚úÖ Failure Root Cause - Detailed error messages and patterns
‚úÖ Trend Analysis - Account-specific trends over time
‚úÖ Comparative Analysis - Compare accounts side-by-side

üéõÔ∏è Interactive Features:
‚úÖ Dynamic Filtering - Select account from dropdown
‚úÖ Multi-Dimensional - Filter by account + OS type
‚úÖ Real-Time Updates - All drill-downs update automatically

Now you can drill down to see exactly which Linux instances in account XYZ need patches, or what specific backup failures are occurring in account ABC! üéØ

