Key Enhancements Added:
üéØ Account Exclusion:
‚úÖ Environment Variable: EXCLUDED_ACCOUNTS - comma-separated list
‚úÖ Lambda Logic: Skips excluded accounts during processing
‚úÖ Logging: Shows which accounts are being excluded

üìä Comprehensive Drill-Down:
‚úÖ All Dashboards: Account filtering on every dashboard
‚úÖ Multi-Dimensional: Filter by account + resource type/OS/severity
‚úÖ Failure Analysis: Merged into backup dashboard with detailed breakdowns

üîç Detailed Metrics Collection:
‚úÖ Account Names: Included in all metrics for better identification
‚úÖ Resource Details: Granular breakdown by type, OS, severity
‚úÖ Failure Analysis: Top failure reasons and failing resources
‚úÖ Cross-Account Comparison: Side-by-side account analysis

‚öôÔ∏è Enhanced Lambda Features:
‚úÖ Robust Error Handling: Comprehensive logging and error recovery
‚úÖ Account Name Resolution: Automatic account name lookup
‚úÖ Detailed Dimensions: Multiple dimensions for precise filtering
‚úÖ Infrastructure Validation: Checks all resources before running

Now you can drill down to see exactly which Linux instances need patches in a specific account, what backup failures are occurring where, and compare accounts side by side! üéØ

